strapiSongs.title: The Disco King
strapiSongs.credits:
• Music by Victor Fisher
• Recorded on November 8 2019
• Published on November 9 2019
• Major remix on December 25 2019
strapiSongs.description:
A psychedelic rock jam that exudes pure coolness at every level.

By the subversive rock band, Reenchantment!

Inspired by Rare Earth’s set at the California Jam in 1974, and Bobby Farrell of Boney M.

![bobby-farrell](http://localhost:1337/uploads/bobby-farrell_ff527d26c8.jpeg)
